sources.title: Stagecoach to Denver
sources.description: Allan Lane is Red Ryder and Robert Blake is Little Beaver in this outing which revolves around a double-crossing stagecoach owner in Elkhorn, Colorado and Dickie (Robert Hyatt), an injured orphan who needs a risky back operation.
